
= "Civil society action to regulate global carbon emissions".

URL = http://www.capglobalcarbon.org


=Description=

"CapGlobalCarbon is a proposal for non-governmental actors to create a new global system to (a) make sure the necessary reductions in total global carbon emissions are achieved and (b) do so in a way that reduces poverty and inequality. The system would operate as a back-up to the inter-governmental negotiations. This idea has been developed by members of the international think tank Feasta."


